attentions.cn: 为保持系统稳定性并确保设备的安全性，近期红米 Note 5 引入了“防回刷”机制。MIUI国内8.7.6及以上的开发版和稳定版V9.5.22及以上版本，将无法降级刷回旧版本的开发版或稳定版。
attentions.en: For maintaining system stability, we've implemented 'Anti-rollback' mechanisim for Redmi Note 5/5 Pro, for China based roms, if your current version is same or higher than 8.7.6 or V9.5.22, then you cannot roll back to older builds.

attentions.cn: 开发版：①8.7.6及以上版本，无法刷回8.7.5及之前的版本（卡刷/线刷均不支持）；②8.7.6及之后的版本之间可互刷，但无法刷回8.7.5或之前版本（卡刷/线刷均不支持）；③8.7.5之前的版本之间仍可互刷
attentions.en: China Beta:①Users with same or higher than 8.7.6 cannot roll back to builds older builds than 8.7.5(Both recovery and fastboot are not supported);② Users can flash builds same or higher that 8.7.6, but can't roll back to older builds(Both recovery and fastboot are not supported);③Users can flash builds older than 8.7.5 freely.

attentions.cn: 稳定版：①V9.5.22及之后的版本，无法刷回V9.5.21之前的版本（卡刷/线刷均不支持）；②V9.5.22及之后的版本之间可互刷，但无法刷回V9.5.21及之前的版本（卡刷/线刷均不支持）；③V9.5.21之前的版本之间仍可互刷
attentions.en: China Mainland Stable:①Users with same or higher than V6.5.22 cannot roll back to builds older builds than V9.5.21(Both recovery and fastboot are not supported);② Users can flash builds same or higher that V9.5.22, but can't roll back to older builds(Both recovery and fastboot are not supported);③Users can flash builds older than V9.5.21 freely.
